title: (Thurs Full) We Reveal Who Got the Movie Role + The Results of The Storage Unit Auction

description:
After a week of buildup, we finally reveal who got the movie role and will be going to Hollywood! Bobby reveals the results of bidding on the storage unit that he and Lunchbox went in on. Did they win? How much did the bidding get up to? Find out!
